description: If you’re suffering from waffle withdrawal, well then you’ve just gotta check out Choctaw’s number one waffle truck, where Chef Jaime is ironing up a sensationally tasty selection of sweet and savory waffle creations. Local favorites include their Grilled Ham & Cheese Sandwich with the option of jalapeno in the batter, The Waffo- cheddar cornbread waffle topped with beans, taco meat, sour cream, salsa, and cheese, and the Cinnawaffle- with yummy homemade icing, to name a few. For all this and more, visit this amazing truck, and if you wish to treat your guests to these warm and buttery beauties, be sure to invite WaffleD to your next big party.
name: WaffleD
